00:46:59,583 --> 00:47:00,777
Sí.

787
00:47:03,587 --> 00:47:06,818
<i>Aquí esta Tom Brokaw en New York.</i>

788
00:47:06,890 --> 00:47:09,484
<i>Buenas tardes. Bill Clinton pudo
